#### Syntax

```
FLUSHDB
```


FLUSHDB deletes all keys present in the database.
	

#### Examples

```

localhost:7379> SET k1 v1
OK
localhost:7379> SET k2 v2
OK
localhost:7379> FLUSHDB
OK
localhost:7379> GET k1
OK ""
localhost:7379> GET k2
OK ""
	
```
